  <section>
    <h1>Documentation</h1>

    <p>
      This documentation describes how BeaconGuard governs execution at the Runtime
      Control Boundary: Compliance Playbooks become Signed Immutable Release Artifacts,
      only an Active Verified Release drives Deterministic Playbook Evaluation, and
      runtime results are ALLOW or DENY before governed execution.
    </p>

    <p>
      Evidence is integrity-protected decision context designed for replay and
      verification. Deployment responsibilities are shared with the customer.
    </p>

